Description
The table contains metrics related to truck utilization over time.  
It includes data on the number of trips completed, total miles driven, 
revenue generated, average miles per gallon, maintenance events, 
associated costs, downtime hours, and the overall utilization rate of each truck.
This information can be used to analyze fleet performance, optimize routes, 
assess maintenance needs, and understand revenue generation trends.

COLUMN                     |                TYPE          |           COMMENT
TRUCK_ID                   |             STRING           |
MONTH                      |             DATE             |
TRIP COMPLETED             |             BIGINT           |
TOTAL_MILES                |             BIGINT           |
TOTAL_REVENUE              |             DOUBLE           |
AVERAGE_MPG                |             DOUBLE           |
MANINTENANCE_EVENT         |             BIGINT           |
MANINTENANCE_COST          |             DOUBLE           |
DOWNTIME HOURS             |             DOUBLE           |
utilization_rate           |             DOUBLE           |


-----SAMPLE DATA
What is the average utilization rate per truck?

--SQL:
      SELECT 
    `truck_id`, 
    AVG(`utilization_rate`) AS `average_utilization_rate` 
FROM 
    `datawerhouse1`.`bronze`.`truck_utilization_metrics` 
GROUP BY 
    `truck_id`

